x4freetext: .SECTOR-FOCUSED ISOCHRONOUS CYCLOTRON.
DISTORED-WAVE IMPULSE APPROXIMATION ANALYSIS.
/BY AUTHORS/.RESULTS FOR K-39 AND N-15 ARE SHOWN AS A
FUNCTION OF THE ENERGY(E)=T(1)+T(2)+T(3),WHERE
T(1) AND T(2) ARE DETECTED PARTICLE KINETIC ENERGIES
AND T(3) IS THE (COMPUTED) RESIDUAL NUCLEUS KINETIC
ENERGY.
/BY COMPILER/.ANG 1 AND ANG 2 IS THE ANGLES OF
OUTGOING PROTONS.
.DATA-POINT READER UNCERTAINTY FOR E.
.THE UNCERTAINTY IS REPORTED BY AUTHORS.
.SEE ABOVE.
.DETECTOR TELESCOPES IN A COPLANAR
GEOMETRY ON BOTH SIDES OF THE INCIDENT BEAM.EACH
TELESCOPE CONSITED OF ONE 540 MUM THICK SILICON
SURFACE BARRIER DETECTOR AND A HIGH PURITY GERMANIUM
STOPPING DETECTOR.
.BY CAJAD.
A NATURAL CALCIUM TARGET WAS USED.
